history.content: Kuch samajh nahi aaya, thoda clarify kar sakti ho? Shayad koi typo hai ya kuch aur kehna chahti ho.
Haha, koi baat nahi, kabhi kabhi shuru se hi ulta chalta hai, kya karein? Thoda patience rakho, sab theek ho jayega. Agar kuch specific poochna ho, toh batao, main hoon na!
Haha, Kuy jani! Kya baat hai, thoda masti ho rahi hai lagta hai. Baat kya hai, koi specific plan banaya hai ya sirf chill kar rahe ho? Batao, sath mein thoda talk karte hain!
Oho, botni ko anj na karne ki koi baat nahi, chhoti si masti hai yeh. Bas yaad rakho, dil se baat karo toh hi dil se samjhegi! Jo bhi karna hai, main yahi hoon na, sath. Tension mat lo, enjoy karo!
